<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Jakob Senfft von Pilsach, Pfleger zu Böheimstein</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Abwesenheit des N. Fleischhacker mit, dessen Ehefrau wegen des Armmanns des Adressaten auf den Rechtsweg verweist, und erklärt sich nach Fleischhackers Rückkehr und Forderung zu dessen Befragung bereit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_204" id="101r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_204_r1l30">Jacob ſenften <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒum Beheımſteın </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_204_r1l31"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Jacob als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des <expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r1l32"><expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſprechen</expan> ſtee / dem einer der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſchuldıg ſey etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r1l33">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Vnd <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> den <expan>fleıſchak<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns den der ewr nennet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r1l34">den es angıeng / beſant vnd <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt Jm <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſo ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r1l35">er auf dıſʒ ʒeıt nıht anheim <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Doch </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_204_line_1577132661328_737">ſo </ab></add> hat ſein <expan>wırtin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_205" id="101v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l1">Jr man . ſey dem <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l2">vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / Doch wenn <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſchak<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heım</expan> kombt ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l3">wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mıt Jm ſelb <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ewch ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>darub<ex>er</ex></expan> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l4">ob wır daran gemant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt </ab>
