</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_204" id="101r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Jacob Senften, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Beheimstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Jacob, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des
                            <expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der ewch <expan>zu
                            v<ex>er</ex>sprechen</expan> stee, dem einer der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> schuldig sey etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>, und <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>Fleischak<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns, den der ewr nennet, den
                        es angieng, besant und <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> mit im
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                        So ist er auf disz zeit niht anheim <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                            <add>so</add> hat sein <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>,<pb facs="#facs_205" id="101v"/> ir man sey dem
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>. Doch wenn
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>Fleischak<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan> kombt, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit im selb
                            <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan> und ewch ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>darub<ex>er</ex></expan> tun, ob wir daran gemant
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
